---
title: Fattoush-Inspired Salad and Chicken Breasts with Spiced Pitas and Feta Cheese
description: Everything about this salad delights! From our beloved shawarma spice blend to the crispy pita and chickpeas, we can't get enough. All that layered with a roasted garlic dressing and tossed with herbs and fresh veg; we know you'll love it as much as we do!
